<entry>
  <title>version 1.1 - Features updates:  Pining and playing</title>
  <updated>2012-09-18</updated>
	<link href="http://btrp.inria.fr/sandbox"/>
	<summary>Two additional features and some bug fixes</summary>
    <content>
        <ul>
            <li>"Pinning" a sandbox allows to save it remotely to re-use it later. Once pinned, it is not possible to change
                the configuration nor the constraints.
            </li>
            <li>A better player to observe the reconfiguration process nicely</li>
            <li>Bug fixes</li>
        </ul>
    </content>
